From: stevev@miser.uoregon.edu (Steve VanDevender)
Subject: Re: New electronic magazine with Linus Torvalds interview
Date: 13 Nov 93 18:54:23

An interesting note: Ghostview 1.5 with Ghostscript 2.6.1 will
only see the first four pages of the Meta magazine Postscript
document.  Ghostview 1.4.1 sees the entire document.  I
discovered this when I downloaded and compiled Ghostview 1.5
after reading the Meta issue with Ghostview 1.4.1.  Fortunately I
stashed the 1.4.1 binary and now have both available.
--
